  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="section section--cream problems">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Kalau you ada soalan ni...</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">You're not alone. Ramai orang ada soalan yang sama.</p>
      <div class="problems__grid">
        <div class="card problems__card">
          <div class="problems__icon">?</div>
          <p>"Am I saving enough?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problems__card">
          <div class="problems__icon">?</div>
          <p>"Is my insurance coverage sufficient?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problems__card">
          <div class="problems__icon">?</div>
          <p>"Macam mana nak start invest?"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problems__card">
          <div class="problems__icon">?</div>
          <p>"Adakah saya buat keputusan kewangan yang betul?"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Target Audience Section -->
  <section class="section audience">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Ini untuk siapa?</h2>
      <div class="audience__grid">
        <div class="card audience__card">
          <div class="audience__emoji">&#127891;</div>
          <h3>Fresh Graduates</h3>
          <p>Yang baru nak mulakan financial journey. Baru kerja, baru ada income — tapi tak tahu nak mula dari mana.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card audience__card">
          <div class="audience__emoji">&#128131;</div>
          <h3>Women Who Want Clarity</h3>
          <p>Women who want to understand their financial situation and take control of their own money with confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card audience__card">
          <div class="audience__emoji">&#127919;</div>
          <h3>Nak Tahu Keadaan Kewangan</h3>
          <p>Anyone yang baru nak start hidup or nak tahu keadaan kewangan sebenar mereka. First step starts here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters Section -->
  <section class="section section--cream why">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Kenapa ramai ada masalah?</h2>
      <div class="why__content">
        <div class="why__text">
          <p class="why__highlight">Masalah bukan pada wang tapi cara nak faham keadaan kewangan.</p>
          <p>Ramai orang ada income yang okay, tapi still rasa lost sebab tak pernah ambil masa untuk truly understand their financial picture.</p>
          <p>Tanpa clarity, you buat keputusan based on assumptions — bukan facts. That's why the first step is always a <strong>Financial Health Check</strong>.</p>
          <p>Once you tahu where you stand, baru you boleh plan with confidence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get Section -->
  <section class="section whatyouget">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Apa yang anda akan dapat?</h2>
      <div class="whatyouget__grid">
        <div class="card whatyouget__card">
          <div class="whatyouget__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>2x Sesi 1:1</h3>
          <p>Two dedicated one-on-one sessions untuk deep dive into your finances. Personalized, bukan generic advice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card whatyouget__card">
          <div class="whatyouget__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>PDF Report</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive analysis of your financial health — everything documented dalam satu report yang jelas dan mudah faham.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card whatyouget__card">
          <div class="whatyouget__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Clear Action Plan</h3>
          <p>Step-by-step action plan yang specific untuk situasi you. No more guessing — you'll know exactly what to do next.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="section section--cream benefits">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Bila you tahu keadaan kewangan you...</h2>
      <div class="benefits__grid">
        <div class="benefits__item">
          <div class="benefits__check">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Make Confident Financial Decisions</h3>
            <p>No more second-guessing. Every decision backed by data and understanding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits__item">
          <div class="benefits__check">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Know Exactly Where Your Money Goes</h3>
            <p>Full visibility on your cash flow, savings, and spending patterns.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits__item">
          <div class="benefits__check">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Clear Direction for Your Financial Future</h3>
            <p>A roadmap yang specific untuk you — bukan generic tips from the internet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Planner Section -->
  <section class="section about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Siapa Iman Abdul Rahim?</h2>
      <div class="about__content">
        <div class="about__info">
          <p class="about__intro">Licensed financial planner with <strong>5 years of experience</strong>, started the CFP journey in 2021. Dedicated to helping Malaysians take control of their finances.</p>
          <div class="about__credentials">
            <h3>Licensed & Regulated</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Licensed by <strong>Securities Commission (SC) Malaysia</strong></li>
              <li>Licensed by <strong>Bank Negara Malaysia</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="about__credentials">
            <h3>Professional Certifications</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>CFP<sup>&reg;</sup> — Certified Financial Planner (FPAM)</li>
              <li>IFP — Islamic Financial Planner (IBFIM)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="about__credentials">
            <h3>Achievements</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Certified Financial Planner FPAM</li>
              <li>Islamic Financial Planner IBFIM</li>
              <li>Accredited HRD Corp Trainer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

